{"tid":827376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雀巢聯合利華可樂傳爭購好立克生產商","createTime":"2018-09-19T01:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T02:12:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6aaa0680aa4e788601ece83a27288b2a97f4db68","tid":827376,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/09/19/1948004_9223adcb7154f1b4b2359c0e49f76913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F1948004_9223adcb7154f1b4b2359c0e49f76913.jpg&h=45067b32&s={SIZE}\" />路透引述消息人士稱，雀巢、聯合利華與可樂，在洽購葛蘭素史克旗下生產好立克(Horlicks)的印度營養品生產分支處於領先地位。該宗交易涉及的金額預期超過40億美元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，葛蘭素史克是以暗標方式出售GlaxoSmithKline Consumer Healthcare的72.5%權益，初次截標時間為周一，雀巢、聯合利華與可樂是三間最可能勝出的買家。<br />\n<br />\n葛蘭素史克、雀巢與聯合利華拒評上述消息。可樂未有回應查詢。<br />\n<br />\nGlaxoSmithKline Consumer Healthcare是在1873年成立的企業，以生產好立克而聞名。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，雀巢長期以來一直想收購好立克。可樂近年來希望將業務多元化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1948004/雀巢聯合利華可樂傳爭購好立克生產商\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1948004%2F%E9%9B%80%E5%B7%A2%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E8%8F%AF%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E5%82%B3%E7%88%AD%E8%B3%BC%E5%A5%BD%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%8B%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%95%86&d=9siJFAaRUHZW6EtVwHtQSlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d6d82273\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1948004/雀巢聯合利華可樂傳爭購好立克生產商</a>"},{"pid":"2796dcf7ff07eaa9936db4fcb9b92277bd7cd7b9","tid":827376,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:28:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得Unilever 機會大<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"52876378f577828859ef2b5991b672bf74460c4b","tid":827376,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2796dcf7ff07eaa9936db4fcb9b92277bd7cd7b9","tid":827376,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T01:28:26.